even if it was ver85

I found the cause. The GPU driver update will solve the problem. Thank you for your support.

issue.body:
Unable to run integration tests in `dev` branch example `integration_test`. ### Error ```console Running "flutter pub get" in example... 4.4s Launching integration_test\example_test.dart on Chrome in debug mode... Waiting for connection from debug service on Chrome... 85.8s Debug service listening on ws://127.0.0.1:59070/XDAfzyVRpJ8=/ws Running with sound null safety Application finished. Unable to start WebDriver Session for Flutter for Web testing. Make sure you have the correct WebDriver Server running at 4444. Make sure the WebDriver Server matches option --browser-name. WebDriverException (404): Error parsing response body: ``` ### Steps to reproduce - Switch to dev branch - cd into `flutter\packages\integration_test\example` - run this command `flutter drive --driver=test_driver\integration_test.dart --target=integration_test\example_test.dart -d chrome --web-port=4444 --browser-name=chrome` ### Other details

issue.title: GPU errors when starting GUI on Ubuntu Linux [Bug]

repository.name: chia-blockchain
repository.description: Chia blockchain python implementation (full node, farmer, harvester, timelord, and wallet)

issue.body:
### What happened?

On an Ubuntu 20.04 VM, fresh OS install, never installed Chia before on this system.
I installed the Chia's .deb using dpkg from the command line.
Upon running chia-blockchain, I got 3 GPU errors (see log output). These errors don't seem to affect Chia, and they may be out of Chia's control. If this is the case, it would be nice to suppress them from showing in the CLI (logging them would be fine) because an end user might think something is wrong with Chia.


### Version

chia-blockchain_1.2.12.dev233_amd64.deb

### What platform are you using?

Linux

### What ui mode are you using?

GUI

### Relevant log output

```shell
djperry@UbuntuNew:~$ chia-blockchain &
[1] 2399
djperry@UbuntuNew:~$ Running python executable: 
child process success
[2433:0202/155659.335365:ERROR:viz_main_impl.cc(162)] Exiting GPU process due to errors during initialization
[2471:0202/155659.410107:ERROR:gpu_init.cc(441)] Passthrough is not supported, GL is swiftshader
[2444:0202/155659.444446:ERROR:command_buffer_proxy_impl.cc(125)] ContextResult::kTransientFailure: Failed to send GpuControl.CreateCommandBuffer.
```
